{
  "texts": [
    "Fan et al. (2019) initially introduced this sub-task and proposed its datasets (FAN 2019).",
    "A target-fused sequence labelling neural network is designed for this task, encoding target information into context using an Inward-Outward LSTM and combining left and right contexts with the global context to identify opinion words.",
    "Experimental results demonstrate the superiority of the proposed model over other methods, potentially benefiting SA and pair-wise opinion summarization.",
    "This task involves classifying the sentence's sentiment towards a particular product or service aspect.",
    "In this example, the sentiment is positive towards the aspect of \"battery life.\""
  ]
}